{
  "chapter": 67,
  "chapter_summary": "齐小燕与吕三在金砖通道中相遇，吕三展示了他的黄金宝库，其中存放着死人和秘密。吕三讲述了一个关于德长老和心眉大师的故事，说明死人可以揭示毒杀秘密。齐小燕被带到宝库深处，看到无数金棺，每个棺材里都有一个死人和一个秘密。吕三解释死人价值远超黄金，可以揭露阴谋。齐小燕感到恐惧但好奇，最终跟随吕三进入宝库。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "想不到你身上居然带着火折子。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "你当然想不到。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "虽然你已经派人把我彻底搜查过，可惜那些人还是没想到我会把一个火折子藏在一个发簪里。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "你身上是不是还藏了些什么别的东西？一些让人想不到的古怪东西？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "如果你想知道，你最好就自己来彻底把我搜查一遍。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "不管怎么样，我都可以跟你保证。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "我身上带着的最古怪最有趣的一样东西，绝不是这个火折子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "我相信。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "我绝对相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "你是不是觉得有点怪怪的？是不是觉得有点不舒服？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "你知不知道你为什么会有这种感觉？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "我怎么想都想不通。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "你知不知道天下万事万物中，最纯最干净的是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "是黄金。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "世上万物，绝没有任何一种比黄金更纯更干净。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "世上也有很多种人，你知不知道最干净的是哪一种？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "是死人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "世上最干净的一种人，就是死人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "你觉得这里有点怪怪的，就因为这里太干净了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "因为这里通常都只有黄金和死人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "这地方是个坟墓？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "坟墓？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "你怎么会想到这里是个坟墓？你怎么会想到我肯用黄金替别人建造坟墓？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "这里究竟是个什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "是个宝库。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "你说这里是个宝库？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "是你藏宝的宝库？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "我可以保证我这里储存的黄金，至少比世上任何一个地方都多三倍。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "如果我将这里的黄金抛售出去，世上每一个国度里黄金的价格都会下落。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "我相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "我这一生中从未见过这么多黄金。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "非但你没有见过，见过这些黄金的人恐怕还没有几个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "因为这里通常都只有死人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "除了很特别的情况之外，这里通常都只有死人才能进来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "你通常都用死人来看守你的黄金？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "自古以来，世上只有一种人会用死人来看守他的黄金。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "哪种人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "死人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "只有死人才会用死人看守他的黄金，因为他已经死了。黄金是不是会被盗走，对他都已不重要。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "可是我没有死，至少现在还没有死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "所以我还不会做这种事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "既然这里是你的宝库，你的宝库里怎么会经常有死人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "就因为这里是宝库。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "所以这里才会有死人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "因为有种死人的价值远比黄金还大得多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "我这里的死人都是这一种。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "在极西的西方，也有一些历史极悠久的古老国家。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "在那些国家里，也有一些学识极渊博的智者。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "我也听说过一点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "那些国家也跟我们一样，也有法律和宗教。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "在他们信奉的宗教里，也有德高望重的长老。就好像我们少林武学的护法长老一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "我知道其中有一位'德长老'，就是个极有智慧、极受人尊敬的人。就好像昔年少林的护法大师'心眉'一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "听说他的师傅是被毒死的。所以他除了精研佛学和武道外，对毒药也研究得极透彻。甚至不惜以肉身遍试百毒，甚至有人说，他到晚年时竞已练成百毒不侵的金刚不坏之身。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "德长老的情况也和心眉大师一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "所以我才会提起他这个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "因为他曾经说过一件非常有趣的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "那位德长老有个非常好的果园，园里种满了各种花卉、水果和蔬菜。他曾经在他的果园里作了一次非常有趣的试验。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "他在果园里选了一种最普通的蔬菜，譬如说是一棵卷心菜，然后他就用一种含有剧毒的蒸馏水，去浇这棵卷心菜。一连浇了三天，卷心菜的叶子就变黄了，而且渐渐枯萎。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "然后他又用这棵卷心菜，去喂一只兔子。三个时辰之后，这只兔子就死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "他叫他的园丁把这个死兔子的内脏，掏出来去喂一只母鸡，第二天母鸡就死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "就在这只母鸡作垂死的挣扎时，恰巧有一只老鹰飞过。在德长老居住的地方，老鹰是很多的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "老鹰把死鸡抓到岩石上，当点心吃了后，就觉得很不舒服。三天后正在空中飞翔时，突然掉了下来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "德长老又要他的园丁找到了这只老鹰，抛入鱼塘里。塘里的鳗鱼、鲤鱼和梭子鱼，都是很贪吃的，当然会把老鹰的肉大吃一顿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "如果说第二天有一尾梭子鱼，被送上你的饭桌去招待你的贵客，那么这位客人在第八天或者第十天之后，就会因肠胃溃烂而死。就算是最有经验的名医和仵作，也绝对检查不出他的死因，更不会想到他是被仇人毒杀而",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 365
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "这个秘密也许永远都不会有人知道，除非……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "除非怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "除非这个死人被送到这里。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "难道你能找出他的死因？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "如果我能及时剖开他的尸体，找到他肠胃中残存的梭子鱼，那么我非但能找出他的死因，而且还能找出毒杀他的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "那么这个死人的价值，就远胜于黄金了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "因为我不但从这个死人身上发现一件本来不会有人知道的秘密，还因此而知道了一种能在不知不觉中将人毒杀致死的巧妙方法。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "毒杀他的那个人的秘密被你发现后，当然也不能不听你的话了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "事情的结果一定就是这样子的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "这个世界上有很多死人都是这样子的。有的中了秘密的毒，有的中了秘密的暗器，有的被人用一种秘密的手法所伤。只要他们的尸体在这里，我就能找出他们致死的秘密。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "对我来说，每一件秘密迟早都会有用的，有时甚至远比黄金有用。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "你愿不愿意去看看我的宝藏？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "我当然愿意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "难道你认为我不敢去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    }
